# Multiplatform Scenarios Challenge


## Add Premium Security to cart
* Navigate to home screen -> See solutions
* Find and click Multiplatform
* Verify if "PREMIUM SECURITY" is selected for multiplatform
* Store prices for "PREMIUM SECURITY"
* Click on buy product "PREMIUM SECURITY"
* Verify that product name is correct
* Verify the correct price and product has been displayed in cart

## Remove product from cart
* From HOMEPAGE insert into cart "PREMIUM SECURITY" and verify it has the correct price displayed in cart
* Delete the product from cart
* Verify if the webpage has returned to product page